{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e81861bcf","title":"中央转发华北局镇反工作指示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d2d54b745e","index":0,"year":1951,"month":6,"day":25,"articleId":"8e81861bcf"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0f7f931aff","type":"title","text":"中央转发华北局镇反工作指示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"0941bba4fb","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"ef84bc6a48","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，并转分局、省市区党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"5d9a145b1d","type":"paragraph","text":"中央完全同意华北局六月二十四日给各省的指示，请你们注意此项问题，并照华北的办法处理之。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"65593dae4d","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央六月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf"}],"page":{"id":"af79d8bccd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8e81861bcf","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"f93290d955","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央华北局在给各省委的指示中指出：各地在传达第三次全国公安会议决议后，曾引起一部分群众以至中下级干部的怀疑、不满与情绪低落。其根本原因，一是传达不深入，简单从事。二是一部分党的领导机关不重视中央公安会议的决议，也不审慎地研究当地当时具体情况，盲目办事。如有的县本来已决定杀掉而又完全应该杀的人，也因收缩杀人权而停止下来。为纠正已经发生和可能发生的上述偏向，各级党委必须大张旗鼓地宣传第三次公安会议的决议，有计划地召开各种会议传达、讲解公安会议的精神，务使家喻户晓，人人明白，以鼓舞广大群众镇反的信心和勇气，巩固并发展镇反成果。同时由于各县区镇反工作发展不平衡，各级党委必须组织力量，一个县、一个区、一个村地去具体检查，具体研究。检查的最好方法就是召开各级的代表会议。"}],"contents":[{"id":"04d84cb318","type":"paragraph","text":"中央完全同意华北局六月二十四日给各省的指示”，请你们注意此项问题，并照华北的办法处理之。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"6e6bb6762c","type":"title","text":"中央转发华北局镇反工作指示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"76c90df042","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"a9935c40ec","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf"},{"id":"f93290d955","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，并转分局、省市区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf"}],"page":{"id":"f7d2765c76","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"8e81861bcf","start":395,"end":395}}}},"__N_SSG":true}